<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>FIREBRAND</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>Stock/Protectorate</FactionKey>
  <Description>ROLE:
FRONTLINE | BRAWLING | TANKING

DIFFICULTY:
EASY

A standard 450mm broadside liner fleet using an intel monitor for awareness and spotting. Your liners offer terrific firepower but are vulnerable in turn; Engagements at long range are your preferred action.

your monitor, Loyal As A Dog, is both vulnerable as well as expensive and important to your fleet. Keeping her safe and alive as long as you can is crucial. If your liners encounter return fire, move up and down to throw off an enemy's aim while opening the range, or go to ground behind a rock to wait for your guns to cycle, before emerging to fire your salvo and retreating back into safety.

&lt;color=blue&gt;Fleet by J4R.&lt;/color&gt;
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder xsi:nil="true" />
